## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-193">호출 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 같은 결과가 설정으로는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-193">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9a064-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 개발자는 초기 문서를 선언적으로 지정 하 여 태그에서 사용 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 때 탐색 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 초기화 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-195">사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> 이스케이프 문자를 포함할 수 있는 URL로 이동 하는 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-195">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9a064-196">사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 으로 이동 하는 메서드는 <xref:System.Uri> 이스케이프 문자를 포함 하지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-197">다음 예제에서는 사용 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다. <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 를 사용 하 여 문서를 탐색 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-197">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-215">사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> 이스케이프 문자를 포함할 수 있는 URL로 이동 하는 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-215">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9a064-216">사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> 으로 이동 하는 메서드는 <xref:System.Uri> 이스케이프 문자를 포함 하지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-217">다음 예제에서는 문서를 탐색 하 고 지정 하 여 새 브라우저 창에서 열에 "에 대 한: 빈" 대상입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-217">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-228">경우는 `stream` 매개 변수는 `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 빈 문서를 탐색 ("에 대 한: 빈").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-228">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-229">Stream 매개 변수는 유효한에 없는 경우 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 형식으로 일반 텍스트로 표시 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-229">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-230">탐색 후 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 됩니다 `null`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-230">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-231">다음 예제에서는 문서를 포함 하는 스트림을 이동 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-231">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-236">경우는 `text` 매개 변수는 `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 빈 문서를 탐색 ("에 대 한: 빈").</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-236">If the `text` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-237">텍스트 매개 변수에 유효한에 없는 경우 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 형식으로 일반 텍스트로 표시 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-237">If the text parameter is not in valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-238">탐색 후 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 됩니다 `null`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-238">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9a064-239">다음 예제에서는 문서를 포함 하는 문자열을 탐색 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9a064-239">The following example shows how to navigate to a string that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStringButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a string  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithoutScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream stream = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  using (StreamReader reader = new StreamReader(stream))  
  {  
    // Navigate to HTML document string  
    this.webBrowser.NavigateToString(reader.ReadToEnd());  
  }  
}  
```
